title: LUNCH Cafe and Eatery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A relaxed cafe offering meals made from whole foods and Alaska ingredients, along with dairy-free and mainly gluten-free baked goods, fresh juices. No red meat. Has Wi-Fi. Opened Jan 2014 at the location of the previous Julia's Solstice Cafe by her family members.
